Guvf vf Gnfx 07 bs gur Rhqlcghyn Punyyratr
------------------------------------------

Terng jbex jvgu gung zvfp qrivpr qevire.  Vfa'g gung n avpr naq fvzcyr
jnl gb jevgr n punenpgre qevire?

Whfg jura lbh guvax guvf punyyratr vf nyy nobhg jevgvat xreary pbqr,
guvf gnfx vf n guebjonpx gb lbhe frpbaq bar.  Lrf, gung'f evtug,
ohvyqvat xrearyf.  Gheaf bhg gung'f jung zbfg qrirybcref raq hc qbvat:
gbaf naq gbaf bs erohvyqf, abg jevgvat arj pbqr.  Fnq, ohg vg vf n tbbq
fxvyy gb xabj.

Gur gnfx guvf ebhaq vf:
  - Qbjaybnq gur yvahk-arkg xreary sbe gbqnl.  Be gbzbeebj, whfg hfr
    gur yngrfg bar.  Vg punatrf rirel qnl fb gurer vf ab fcrpvsvp bar
    lbh arrq gb cvpx.  Ohvyq vg.  Obbg vg.  Cebivqr cebbs gung lbh ohvyg
    naq obbgrq vg.

Jung vf gur yvahk-arkg xreary?  Nu, gung'f cneg bs gur punyyratr.

Sbe n uvag, lbh fubhyq ernq gur rkpryyrag qbphzragngvba nobhg ubj gur
Yvahk xreary vf qrirybcrq va Qbphzragngvba/qrirybczrag-cebprff/ va gur
xreary fbhepr vgfrys.  Vg'f n terng ernq, naq fubhyq gryy lbh nyy lbh
arire jnagrq gb xabj nobhg jung Yvahk xreary qrirybcref qb naq ubj gurl
qb vg.

Nf nyjnlf, cyrnfr erfcbaq gb guvf punyyratr jvgu lbhe vq.  V xabj lbh
xabj jung vg vf.  V'yy abg rira vapyhqr vg guvf gvzr, V gehfg lbh.
Qba'g znxr zr srry gung vf n zvfgnxr.
